data.title: V. Rama Naidu And Another vs Smt. V.Ramadevi
data.meta_description: V. Rama Naidu And Another vs Smt. V.Ramadevi
data.text: All Words Territorial Jurisdiction System will search all the judgements wherein both the words Territorial and Jurisdiction exist. Both the words Territorial and Jurisdiction might or might not be together in the search results. Usage of Near in All Words Murder Weapon Not Found @Near 10 System will search for judgements wherein all the words in the String "Murder Weapon Not Found" are present and are not separated by more than 10 words Territorial Jurisdiction System will search the exact phrase "Territorial Jurisdiction" i.e. the outcome will be all the judgements wherein both the words Territorial Jurisdiction are together. OR "Territorial Jurisdiction" OR "Section 138 NI Act" System will search for judgements wherein either or both of the phrases (I.e. "Teritorial Jurisdiction" or "Section 138 NI Act" are present as it is. AND "Territorial Jurisdiction" AND "Section 138 NI Act" System will search for judgements wherein both the phrases (I.e. "Teritorial Jurisdiction" and "Section 138 NI Act") are present as it is.
